### Todo Task API — Tasks (Bearer required; JWT sub = owner)
### Run Google auth first and paste accessToken below.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3008/api/v1
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
@taskId = TASK_UUID_FROM_CREATE_OR_LIST

### List tasks (paginated + optional title search)
GET http://localhost:3008/api/v1/tasks?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhODYwNWMwNS1iZmIwLTQ5YzItYTdlNS04MzdhYzMxNGY0NDMiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJhbWlrZWZhYWRld2FsZUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJzZXNzaW9uSWQiOiIyNjRmYzNjZC1lZTJmLTQ3ZWEtYjAwNC0yYzNlMjZkZmJiMDQiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3MDA4NDIsImV4cCI6MTc3NDc4NzI0MiwiYXVkIjoibG9jYWxob3N0OjMwMDgiLCJpc3MiOiJsb2NhbGhvc3Q6MzAwOCJ9.Afn30NFjJCcTc5asuWhpkiM0xeN0Szl7Qi6QBQxlb6s

### List tasks — search
GET http://localhost:3008/api/v1/tasks?page=1&pageSize=10&q=my
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhODYwNWMwNS1iZmIwLTQ5YzItYTdlNS04MzdhYzMxNGY0NDMiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJhbWlrZWZhYWRld2FsZUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJzZXNzaW9uSWQiOiIyNjRmYzNjZC1lZTJmLTQ3ZWEtYjAwNC0yYzNlMjZkZmJiMDQiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3MDA4NDIsImV4cCI6MTc3NDc4NzI0MiwiYXVkIjoibG9jYWxob3N0OjMwMDgiLCJpc3MiOiJsb2NhbGhvc3Q6MzAwOCJ9.Afn30NFjJCcTc5asuWhpkiM0xeN0Szl7Qi6QBQxlb6s

### Create task (201 + Task body)
# @name createTask
POST http://localhost:3008/api/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhODYwNWMwNS1iZmIwLTQ5YzItYTdlNS04MzdhYzMxNGY0NDMiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImJhbWlrZWZhYWRld2FsZUBnbWFpbC5jb20iLCJzZXNzaW9uSWQiOiIyNjRmYzNjZC1lZTJmLTQ3ZWEtYjAwNC0yYzNlMjZkZmJiMDQiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ3MDA4NDIsImV4cCI6MTc3NDc4NzI0MiwiYXVkIjoibG9jYWxob3N0OjMwMDgiLCJpc3MiOiJsb2NhbGhvc3Q6MzAwOCJ9.Afn30NFjJCcTc5asuWhpkiM0xeN0Szl7Qi6QBQxlb6s
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy groceries"
}

### Toggle task done
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
